{"tid":846081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美戰艦南海「交鋒」照片曝光　陸艦從後逼近　相差幾秒就相撞","createTime":"2018-10-03T07:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T12:15:08.000Z","uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72066140ddac3e51be10c752fd2adcab3d2b9d12","tid":846081,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/navy_1ltnq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnavy_1ltnq_1200x0.png&h=33491382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國驅逐艦 Decatur 在周日（9月30日）駛入南海南薰礁（Gaven）及赤瓜礁（Johnson）12海浬內海域時，與一艘中國驅逐艦近距離「交鋒」。事發一刻的相片今日流出，可見中美兩國艦隻極為接近，中方艦隻從後逼近美國驅逐艦。<br />\n<br />\n有三位美國官員向CNN證實，四張相片的確是由美國海軍所拍攝，但官方未有循正式途徑發相。相片最先在一個名為個「gCaptain」的網站上發表，網站形容自己是一個「海事專業人士的互動社區」。<br />\n<br />\n據美國CNN報道，由美國海軍拍攝的航拍照片顯示，一艘美國海軍艦艇與一艘中國軍艦距離極為接近，解放軍導彈驅逐艦蘭州號正從後方逼近美國驅逐艦 Decatur。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E6%88%B0%E8%89%A6%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7-%E4%BA%A4%E9%8B%92-%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE%E5%B9%BE%E7%A7%92%E5%B0%B1%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%2589%25A6%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%258B%2592-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E7%25A7%2592%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E%2F&d=MleP2A74iKeYqMitjt%2BqW%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8ed2ddd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%2589%25A6%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%258B%2592-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E7%25A7%2592%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2592%259E%2F&h=1fa13011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E6%88%B0%E8%89%A6%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7-%E4%BA%A4%E9%8B%92-%E4%BA%8B%E7%99%BC%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE%E5%B9%BE%E7%A7%92%E5%B0%B1%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E/</a>"},{"pid":"ffc9fb4311942a6ddad5e292740e4aeb64358667","tid":846081,"uid":193613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"撞先算喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa823c21352290abcdd99d6a84569ee8e63a10fd","tid":846081,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"中方又話係美方艦艇撞過黎？"},{"pid":"af7d31de3c1cdb043d70f3487abaea7ecef76838","tid":846081,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"又賓州爛，又爛州號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}